    Page: 8
    Verse: 6
Tags:
  - Adversity
---
The only way to know truly is through practical experiment and experience.
Theory and speculation, if they are not followed by trial and
demonstration, are useless. ...Knowledge itself is of little or no value if
it does not lead to action.
